(1107,0,'npc_gossip','textid','This references the “npc_text” tables unique ID.','This references the “npc_text” tables unique ID of the NPC text for which the entry is valid.<br /><br /><b>Note:</b><br />To actually make a creature display a gossip dialogue with the linked text, you will have to update the “creature_template” table as follows:<br /><pre>SET @CREATURE_FLAG_NPC_GOSSIP                   = 1;<br /><br />UPDATE `creature_template`<br />SET<br />    `NpcFlags`              = `NpcFlags` | @CREATURE_FLAG_NPC_GOSSIP,<br />WHERE<br />    `entry`                 = YOUR-CREATURE;<br /></pre>This will add the gossip flag to any existing flags and thus enable the link text to be displayed.'),
